		]a
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 
	" Essentials
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		" Aims for lowest score (primary goal), and fastest time
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Takes damage to get lower score, or save time
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Uses a game restart sequence
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		" Emulator used is 
		[a class=intlink href=/EmulatorResources/Snes9x 
			"Snes9x 1.43 rerecording
		]a
		" v9 (v17 is also supported)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Let the ROM run for a few seconds before playing the movie
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		" Use WIP1 Timing: ON (IMPORTANT)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Allow Left+Right / Up+Down: ON (IMPORTANT)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Volume Envelope Height Reading: ON
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Fake Mute desync workaround: OFF
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Sync samples with sound CPU: ON
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 
	" About the game
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Kirby's Dream Course (known as カービィボウル in Japan) is a very innovative golf game.
	$LF
	"The game combines elements from the Kirby series (enemies, environments, and Kirby's 
	$LF
	"ability to absorb skills) with the rules of golf, creating in a unique style of gameplay.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"For details, see 
	[a class=extlink href=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kirby%27s_Dream_Course rel=nofollow 
		"Wikipedia:Kirby's Dream Course
	]a
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Don't be fooled, this game is harder than it looks.
	$LF
]p
